---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import PageHeader from '~/components/PageHeader.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="關於 CHIEN"
  description="CHIEN 的個人介紹，包含學習背景、技能、網路技術與資訊安全興趣，以及目前參與的實習與社群經歷。"
  pageType="profile"
>
  <PageHeader>About</PageHeader>
  <div class="max-w-full py-7.5 prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert about-page">

    <h2>嗨！我是 CHIEN</h2>
    <p>
      你可以叫我柴柴或是 CHIEN，但大部分人都叫我柴柴或是柴<br />
      一個出生在台灣的 <del>高職生</del> 大學生，目前就讀<strong>國立宜蘭大學資訊工程系</strong>
    </p>

    <h2>我在做什麼</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>運營個人自治系統 <strong>AS215934</strong>，研究 BGP 路由協議</li>
      <li>專注於資訊安全、網路運維與系統架構</li>
      <li>目前在<strong>瀚霖智動銷售科技</strong>擔任實習工程師，負責系統維運、資安與全端開發</li>
      <li>曾在 SITCON 擔任多個職位，從志工、副組長到副召，2026 年將擔任總召</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>技能樹</h2>
    <div class="not-prose space-y-5">
      <!-- Languages & Frameworks -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-3">Languages & Frameworks</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-5 md:grid-cols-7 gap-2 items-start">
          {[
            { name: 'Python',      icon: 'python/python-original' },
            { name: 'JavaScript',  icon: 'javascript/javascript-original' },
            { name: 'TypeScript',  icon: 'typescript/typescript-original' },
            { name: 'C++',         icon: 'cplusplus/cplusplus-original' },
            { name: 'C#',          icon: 'csharp/csharp-original' },
            { name: 'Go',          icon: 'go/go-original-wordmark' },
            { name: 'Swift',       icon: 'swift/swift-original' },
            { name: 'Vue.js',      icon: 'vuejs/vuejs-original' },
            { name: 'React',       icon: 'react/react-original' },
            { name: 'Django',      icon: 'django/django-plain' },
            { name: 'TailwindCSS', icon: 'tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original' },
          ].map(skill => (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 p-2 rounded-lg border border-separator bg-background hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors">
              <img
                src={`https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/${skill.icon}.svg`}
                alt={skill.name}
                class="w-8 h-8 object-contain not-prose"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-center leading-tight">{skill.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Systems & Infra -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-3">Systems & Infra</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-5 md:grid-cols-7 gap-2 items-start">
          {[
            { name: 'Linux',   icon: 'linux/linux-original' },
            { name: 'Windows', icon: 'windows11/windows11-original' },
            { name: 'Docker',  icon: 'docker/docker-original' },
            { name: 'Git',     icon: 'git/git-original' },
            { name: 'Nginx',   icon: 'nginx/nginx-original' },
          ].map(skill => (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 p-2 rounded-lg border border-separator bg-background hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors">
              <img
                src={`https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/${skill.icon}.svg`}
                alt={skill.name}
                class="w-8 h-8 object-contain not-prose"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-center leading-tight">{skill.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 p-2 rounded-lg border border-separator bg-background hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors">
            <img src="/icons/bgp.svg" alt="BGP" class="w-8 h-8 object-contain not-prose" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-center leading-tight">BGP</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 p-2 rounded-lg border border-separator bg-background hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors">
            <img src="/icons/networking.svg" alt="網路運維" class="w-8 h-8 object-contain not-prose" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-center leading-tight">網路運維</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>找我聊天</h2>
    <p>想討論網路技術、資安或是任何有趣的專案嗎？歡迎來找我！</p>

    <p>
      <img src="https://discord-readme-badge.vercel.app/api?id=679496165183586335" alt="Discord Badge" loading="lazy" />
    </p>

    <p>
      Email: <a href="mailto:hi@chien.dev">hi@chien.dev</a><br />
      GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/qian403" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@qian403</a><br />
      Telegram: <a href="https://t.me/qian50" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@qian50</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page :is(h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6)::before {
    content: '' !important;
  }
</style>
